Hi,

I'm currently trying to speed up the compilation of the verilated C++ model from a large netlist.

I successfuly asked Verilator to split the model into many cpp files : 

```
 --output-split 5000
 --output-split-cfuncs 500
 --output-split-ctrace 500
``` 

But when i make the xxx.mk generated by verilator, all those verilated cpp files are compiled as a single cpp via the generated Vxxx__ALLcls.cpp : 

```
